      "value": "<p>For lighting I did a simple 3 point lighting using Disk lights for Key and Fill light and a Rect light for Rim light. I added another Disk light with lower intensity to get the specular in the Right eye.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"image15.png\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657850369/image15.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762593387009&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=383\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/657850369/image15.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762593387009&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"709\" data-width=\"1406\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657850381\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"image15.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"657850369\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"7b723945-aff2-40cf-bc89-f17aa19fb930\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657850369/image15.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762593387009&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=766 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657850369/image15.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762593387009&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=383 1x\"></span><p /><p>And Finally... Here we are!</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"image21.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/down